[[Translation:Main/en/Train income warning]]
This option will present a warning as a news message if a train's income has been negative recently, to enable you to find out why and correct the situation.

Note that this setting has been renamed from [[Main/en/Configuring patches/Vehicles#Warn if a train's income is negative|Warn if a train's income is negative]] since OpenTTD 0.7.0.

To prevent this warning when operating a [[Main/en/Feeder service|feeder service]], see [[Main/en/Negative income with feeder service]].
